&amp;=F_1 \delta u_1 + (F_2 + F_3 \sin \theta) \delta u_2 +

\end{align*}

由Hamilton原理

$$\int \delta T - \delta V + \delta W_{nc} = 0$$

动能

$$
\begin{align*}
T &amp;= \frac{1}{2}m_1 \dot u_1^2 + \frac{1}{2}m_2 \dot u_2^2 + \frac{1}{2}m_3 (v_{x3}^2 + v_{y3}^2) \\
&amp;= \frac{1}{2}m_1 \dot u_1^2 + \frac{1}{2}m_2 \dot u_2^2 + \frac{1}{2}m_3 ((L \dot \theta \cos \theta)^2 + (\dot u_2 + L \dot \theta \sin \theta)^2) \\
&amp;= \frac{1}{2}m_1 \dot u_1^2 + \frac{1}{2}m_2 \dot u_2^2 + \frac{1}{2}m_3 (\dot u_2^2 + 2 \dot u_2 L \dot \theta \sin \theta + L^2 \dot \theta^2)
\end{align*}
$$

则

$$
\delta T = m_1 \dot u_1 \delta \dot u_1 + m_2 \dot u_2 \delta \dot u_2 + m_3 \dot u_2 \delta \dot u_2 + m_3 L \dot \theta \sin \theta \delta \dot u_2 + m_3 \dot u_2 L \sin \theta \delta \dot \theta + m_3 \dot u_2 L \dot \theta \cos \theta \delta \theta + m_3 L^2 \dot \theta \delta \dot \theta
$$

势能

$$
\begin{align*}
V &amp;= \frac{1}{2} k_1 u_1^2 + \frac{1}{2} k_2 (u_2 - u_1)^2 + m_1 g u_1 + m_2 g u_2 + m_3 g (u_2 - L \cos \theta)
\end{align*}
$$

则

$$
\delta V = k_1 u_1 \delta u_1 + k_2(u_2 - u_1)(\delta u_2 - \delta u_1) + m_1 g \delta u_1 + m_2 g \delta u_2 + m_3 g(\delta u_2 + L \sin \theta \delta \theta) 
$$

非保守力做功

$$
\begin{align*}
\delta W_{nc} &amp;= F_1 \delta u_1 + F_2 \delta u_2 + \vec F_3 \cdot \delta \vec r_3 \\
&amp;=F_1 \delta u_1 + F_2 \delta u_2 + (F_3 \cos \theta (L \cos \theta \delta \theta) + F_3\sin\theta (\delta u_2 + L \sin \theta \delta \theta)) \\
&amp;=F_1 \delta u_1 + (F_2 + F_3 \sin \theta) \delta u_2 + 
F_3 L\delta \theta \\
\end{align*}
$$

所以

$$
\begin{align*}
\int \delta T - \delta V + \delta W_{nc} &amp;= \int_{t_1}^{t_2} ( m_1 \dot u_1 \delta \dot u_1 + m_2 \dot u_2 \delta \dot u_2 + m_3 \dot u_2 \delta \dot u_2 + m_3 L \dot \theta \sin \theta \delta \dot u_2 + m_3 \dot u_2 L \sin \theta \delta \dot \theta + m_3 \dot u_2 L \dot \theta \cos \theta \delta \theta + m_3 L^2 \dot \theta \delta \dot \theta\\
&amp;\quad - ( k_1 u_1 \delta u_1 + k_2(u_2 - u_1)(\delta u_2 - \delta u_1) + m_1 g \delta u_1 + m_2 g \delta u_2 + m_3 g(\delta u_2 + L \sin \theta \delta \theta) ) \\
&amp;\quad + F_1 \delta u_1 + (F_2 + F_3 \sin \theta) \delta u_2 + F_3 L\delta \theta )d t\\
&amp;= m_1 \dot u_1 \delta u_1 \big |_{t_1}^{t_2} - \int_{t_1}^{t_2}m_1 \ddot u_1 \delta u_1 dt + m_2 \dot u_2 \delta u_2 \big |_{t_1}^{t_2} - \int_{t_1}^{t_2}m_2 \ddot u_2 \delta u_2 dt + m_3 \dot u_2 \delta u_2 \big |_{t_1}^{t_2} - \int_{t_1}^{t_2}m_3 \ddot u_2 \delta u_2 dt \\
&amp;\quad + m_3 L \dot \theta \sin \theta \delta u_2 \big |_{t_1}^{t_2} - \int_{t_1}^{t_2}(m_3 L \ddot \theta \sin \theta + m_3 L \dot \theta^2 \cos \theta) \delta u_2dt \\
&amp;\quad+ m_3 L \dot u_2 \sin \theta \delta \theta \big |_{t_1}^{t_2} - \int_{t_1}^{t_2}(m_3 L \ddot u_2 \sin \theta + m_3 L \dot u_2\dot \theta \cos \theta) \delta \theta dt\\
&amp;\quad + \int_{t_1}^{t_2} m_3 \dot u_2 L \dot \theta \cos \theta \delta \theta d t \\
&amp;\quad + m_3 L^2 \dot \theta \delta \theta \big |_{t_1}^{t_2} - \int_{t_1}^{t_2}m_3 L^2 \ddot \theta \delta \theta dt \\
&amp;\quad \int_{t_1}^{t_2} - ( k_1 u_1 \delta u_1 + k_2(u_2 - u_1)(\delta u_2 - \delta u_1) + m_1 g \delta u_1 + m_2 g \delta u_2 + m_3 g(\delta u_2 + L \sin \theta \delta \theta) ) \\
&amp;\quad + F_1 \delta u_1 + (F_2 + F_3 \sin \theta) \delta u_2 + F_3 L\delta \theta )d t\\
&amp;= -\int_{t_1}^{t_2}(m_1 \ddot u_1 + (k_1+k_2) u_1 - k_2 u_2 + m_1 g - F_1 )dt \\
&amp;\quad - \int_{t_1}^{t_2}((m_2 + m_3) \ddot u_2 + m_3 L \ddot \theta \sin \theta + m_3 L \dot \theta^2 \cos \theta - k_2 u_1 + k_2 u_2 + (m_2 + m_3) g - F_2 - F_3 \sin \theta)dt \\
&amp;\quad -\int_{t_1}^{t_2}(m_3 \ddot u_2 L \sin \theta + m_3 L^2 \ddot \theta + m_3 g L \sin \theta - F_3L)dt \\
&amp;= 0
\end{align*}
$$

由$u_1, u_2, \theta$任意性有

$$
\begin{cases}
m_1 \ddot u_1 + (k_1+k_2) u_1 - k_2 u_2 + m_1 g &amp;= F_1 \\
(m_2 + m_3) \ddot u_2 + m_3 L \ddot \theta \sin \theta + m_3 L \dot \theta^2 \cos \theta - k_2 u_1 + k_2 u_2 + (m_2 + m_3) g &amp;= F_2 + F_3 \sin \theta\\
m_3 \ddot u_2 L \sin \theta + m_3 L \ddot \theta + m_3 g L^2 \sin \theta &amp;= F_3L
\end{cases}
$$"><h2>1.1</h2><p>由Hamilton原理</p><p></p><div class="MathJax" display="block" style="text-align:center;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22.515ex" height="5.027ex" role="img" 平衡的时候有$\ddot u_1 = \ddot u_2 = \ddot \theta = \dot u_1 = \dot u_2 = \dot \theta = 0$, 代入方程有:

$$
\begin{cases}
(k_1+k_2) u_1 - k_2 u_2 + m_1 g &amp;= F_1 \\
-k_2 u_1 + k_2 u_2 + (m_2 + m_3) g &amp;= F_2 + F_3 \sin \theta\\
m_3 g L \sin \theta &amp;= F_3L
\end{cases}
$$

解得

$$
\begin{cases}
u_1 &amp;= \frac{(F_1 + F_2) m_3 g + F_3^2 - (m_1 + m_2 + m_3)m_3g^2}{k_1 m_3 g} \\
u_2 &amp;= \frac{k_2 F_1 m_3 g + (k_1 + k_2)F_2 m_3 g + (k_1+k_2)F_3^2 - k_2(m_1+m_2+m_3)m_3g^2 - k_1 (m_2+m_3) m_3 g^2}{k_1 k_2 m_3 g}\\
\theta &amp;= \arcsin \frac {F_3} {m_3 g}
\end{cases}
$$

若初始时$F_i= 0$, 则有

$$
\begin{cases}
u_1^\star &amp;= \frac{- (m_1 + m_2 + m_3)g}{k_1} \\
u_2^\star &amp;= \frac{ - k_2(m_1+m_2+m_3)g - k_1 (m_2 + m_3)g}{k_1 k_2}\\
\theta^\star &amp;= 0
\end{cases}
$$"><h2>1.3</h2><p>平衡的时候有<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="30.483ex" height="2.67ex" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 -1030 13473.5 1180" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" 考虑平衡位置

$$
\begin{cases}
u_1^\star &amp;= \frac{(F_1 + F_2) m_3 g + F_3^2 - (m_1 + m_2 + m_3)m_3g^2}{k_1 m_3 g} \\
u_2^\star &amp;= \frac{k_2 F_1 m_3 g + (k_1 + k_2)F_2 m_3 g + (k_1+k_2)F_3^2 - k_2(m_1+m_2+m_3)m_3g^2 - k_1 (m_2+m_3) m_3 g^2}{k_1 k_2 m_3 g}\\
\theta^\star &amp;= \arcsin \frac {F_3} {m_3 g}
\end{cases}
$$

平衡位置处线性化, 令

$$
\begin{cases}
\hat u_1 &amp;= u_1^\star + u_1 \\
\hat u_2 &amp;= u_2^\star + u_2 \\
\hat \theta &amp;= \theta^\star + \theta
\end{cases}
$$

且有

$$
\begin{align*}
\sin \theta \rightarrow \theta \\
\cos \theta \rightarrow 1 \\
\dot \theta^2 \rightarrow 0 \\
\ddot \theta \theta \rightarrow 0
\end{align*}
$$

化简则有

$$
\begin{cases}
m_1 \ddot u_1 + (k_1+k_2) u_1 - k_2 u_2 &amp;= F_1 \\
(m_2 + m_3) \ddot u_2 - k_2 u_1 + k_2 u_2 &amp;= F_2 + F_3 \sin \theta \\
m_3 L^2 \ddot \theta + m_3 g L \theta &amp;= F_3L
\end{cases}
$$

写出矩阵形式:

$$
\begin{bmatrix}
m_1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; m_2 + m_3 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; m_3 L^2
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
\ddot u_1 \\
\ddot u_2 \\
\ddot \theta
\end{bmatrix}
+
\begin{bmatrix}
k_1 + k_2 &amp; -k_2 &amp; 0 \\
-k_2 &amp; k_2 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; m_3 g L
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
u_1 \\
u_2 \\
\theta
\end{bmatrix}
=\begin{bmatrix}
F_1 \\
F_2 + F_3 \sin \theta \\
F_3L
\end{bmatrix}
$$

由题意$F_i = 0$

$$
\begin{bmatrix}
m_1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; m_2 + m_3 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; m_3 L^2
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
\ddot u_1 \\
\ddot u_2 \\
\ddot \theta
\end{bmatrix}
+
\begin{bmatrix}
k_1 + k_2 &amp; -k_2 &amp; 0 \\
-k_2 &amp; k_2 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; m_3 g L
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
u_1 \\
u_2 \\
\theta
\end{bmatrix}
=0
$$


由于$m_i = m, k_i = k$, 则

$$
M = \begin{bmatrix}
m &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 2m &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; m L^2
\end{bmatrix}
$$

$$
K = \begin{bmatrix}
2 k &amp; -k &amp; 0 \\
-k &amp; k &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; m g L
\end{bmatrix}
$$

特征方程

$$|K - \lambda M | = ( m L^2 \lambda - m g L) (2 m^2 \lambda^2 - 5 k m \lambda + k^2) = 0$$

解得

$$
\begin{cases}
\lambda_1 &amp;= \frac{5 - \sqrt{17} }{4 } \frac{k}{m} \\
\lambda_2 &amp;= \frac{5 + \sqrt{17}}{4 } \frac{k}{m} \\
\lambda_3 &amp;= \frac{g}{L} \\
\end{cases}
$$

特征向量为

$$
\begin{cases}
u_1 &amp;= c_1 \begin{bmatrix}
\frac{-3 + \sqrt{17} }{2} \\
1 \\
0
\end{bmatrix} \\
u_2 &amp;= c_2 \begin{bmatrix}
\frac{-3 - \sqrt{17} }{2} \\
1 \\
0
\end{bmatrix} \\
u_3 &amp;= c_3 \begin{bmatrix}
0 \\
0 \\
1
\end{bmatrix} \\
\end{cases}
$$"><h2>1.4</h2><p>考虑平衡位置</p><p></p><div class="MathJax" display="block" style="text-align:center;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="65.659ex" height="11.528ex" role="img" div.data-content:
## 1.2

动能

$$
\begin{align*}
T &= \frac{1}{2}m_1 \dot u_1^2 + \frac{1}{2}m_2 \dot u_2^2 + \frac{1}{2}m_3 (v_{x3}^2 + v_{y3}^2) \\
&= \frac{1}{2}m_1 \dot u_1^2 + \frac{1}{2}m_2 \dot u_2^2 + \frac{1}{2}m_3 ((L \dot \theta \cos \theta)^2 + (\dot u_2 + L \dot \theta \sin \theta)^2) \\
&= \frac{1}{2}m_1 \dot u_1^2 + \frac{1}{2}m_2 \dot u_2^2 + \frac{1}{2}m_3 (\dot u_2^2 + 2 \dot u_2 L \dot \theta \sin \theta + L^2 \dot \theta^2)
\end{align*}
$$

势能

$$
\begin{align*}
V &= \frac{1}{2} k_1 u_1^2 + \frac{1}{2} k_2 (u_2 - u_1)^2 + m_1 g u_1 + m_2 g u_2 + m_3 g (u_2 - L \cos \theta)
\end{align*}
$$

div.style: display: flex; align-items: unsafe center; justify-content: unsafe flex-start; width: 1px; height: 1px; padding-top: 1304px; margin-left: 533px;
box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 0px; text-align: left;
display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.2; pointer-events: all; white-space: nowrap;

div.data-content:
由

$$
\begin{cases}
x_3 &= L \sin \theta \\
y_3 &= u_2 - L \cos \theta \\
\end{cases}
$$

得

$$
\begin{cases}
v_{x3} &= L \dot \theta \cos \theta \\
v_{y3} &= \dot u_2 + L \dot \theta \sin \theta \\
\end{cases}
$$

div.style: display: flex; align-items: unsafe center; justify-content: unsafe flex-start; width: 1px; height: 1px; padding-top: 1569px; margin-left: 13px;
box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 0px; text-align: left;
display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.2; pointer-events: all; white-space: nowrap;

div.data-content:
非保守力做功

$$
\begin{align*}
\delta W_{nc} &= F_1 \delta u_1 + F_2 \delta u_2 + \vec F_3 \cdot \delta \vec r_3 \\
&=F_1 \delta u_1 + F_2 \delta u_2 + (F_3 \cos \theta (L \cos \theta \delta \theta) + F_3\sin\theta (\delta u_2 + L \sin \theta \delta \theta)) \\
&=F_1 \delta u_1 + (F_2 + F_3 \sin \theta) \delta u_2 +
F_3 L\delta \theta \\
\end{align*}
$$

所以

$$
\begin{cases}
Q_1 &= F_1 \\
Q_2 &= F_2 + F_3 \sin \theta \\
Q_3 &= F_3L
\end{cases}
$$

div.style: display: flex; align-items: unsafe center; justify-content: unsafe flex-start; width: 1px; height: 1px; padding-top: 1539px; margin-left: 533px;
box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 0px; text-align: left;
display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.2; pointer-events: all; white-space: nowrap;

div.data-content:
$$
\vec F_3 = (F_3 \cos \theta, F_3 \sin \theta)
$$

$$
\begin{cases}
\vec F_3 &= (F_3 \cos \theta, F_3 \sin \theta) \\
\vec r_3 &= (L \sin \theta, u_2 - L \cos \theta) \\
\end{cases}
$$

div.style: display: flex; align-items: unsafe center; justify-content: unsafe flex-start; width: 1px; height: 1px; padding-top: 1764px; margin-left: 2px;
box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 0px; text-align: left;
display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.2; pointer-events: all; white-space: nowrap;

div.data-content:
由拉格朗日方程

$$\frac {\partial }{ \partial t} \frac {\partial L}{ \partial \dot q} - \frac {\partial L}{ \partial q} = Q$$

$$
\begin{align*}
L &= T - V \\
&= \frac{1}{2}m_1 \dot u_1^2 + \frac{1}{2}m_2 \dot u_2^2 + \frac{1}{2}m_3 (\dot u_2^2 + 2 \dot u_2 L \dot \theta \sin \theta + L \dot \theta^2) - (\frac{1}{2} k_1 u_1^2 + \frac{1}{2} k_2 (u_2 - u_1)^2 + m_1 g u_1 + m_2 g u_2 + m_3 g (u_2 - L \cos \theta) )
\end{align*}
$$

div.style: display: flex; align-items: unsafe center; justify-content: unsafe flex-start; width: 1px; height: 1px; padding-top: 1909px; margin-left: 33px;
box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 0px; text-align: left;
display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.2; pointer-events: all; white-space: nowrap;

div.data-content:
$$
\begin{cases}
\frac {\partial L}{ \partial \dot u_1} &= m_1 \dot u_1 \\
\frac {\partial L}{ \partial \dot u_2} &= m_2 \dot u_2 + m_3 \dot u_2 + m_3 L \dot \theta \sin \theta\\
\frac {\partial L}{ \partial \dot \theta} &= m_3 \dot u_2 L \sin \theta + m_3 L^2 \dot \theta
\end{cases}
$$

div.style: display: flex; align-items: unsafe center; justify-content: unsafe flex-start; width: 1px; height: 1px; padding-top: 1909px; margin-left: 387px;
box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 0px; text-align: left;
display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.2; pointer-events: all; white-space: nowrap;

div.data-content:
$$
\begin{cases}
\frac {\partial }{ \partial t} \frac {\partial L}{ \partial \dot u_1} &= m_1 \ddot u_1 \\
\frac {\partial }{ \partial t} \frac {\partial L}{ \partial \dot u_2} &= m_2 \ddot u_2 + m_3 \ddot u_2 + m_3 L \ddot \theta \sin \theta + m_3 L \dot \theta^2 \cos \theta\\
\frac {\partial }{ \partial t} \frac {\partial L}{ \partial \dot \theta} &= m_3 \ddot u_2 L \sin \theta + m_3 \dot u_2 \dot \theta L \cos \theta + m_3 L^2 \ddot \theta
\end{cases}
$$

div.style: display: flex; align-items: unsafe center; justify-content: unsafe flex-start; width: 1px; height: 1px; padding-top: 2009px; margin-left: 33px;
box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 0px; text-align: left;
display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.2; pointer-events: all; white-space: nowrap;

div.data-content:
$$
\begin{cases}
\frac {\partial L}{ \partial u_1} &= -(k_1 u_1 + k_2 (u_1 - u_2) + m_1 g ) \\
\frac {\partial L}{ \partial u_2} &= -(k_2(u_2 - u_1) + m_2 g + m_3 g)\\
\frac {\partial L}{ \partial \theta} &= m_3 \dot u_2 L \dot \theta \cos \theta -(m_3 g L \sin \theta)
\end{cases}
$$

div.style: display: flex; align-items: unsafe center; justify-content: unsafe flex-start; width: 1px; height: 1px; padding-top: 2114px; margin-left: 63px;
box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 0px; text-align: left;
display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.2; pointer-events: all; white-space: nowrap;

div.data-content:
代入得到

$$
\begin{cases}
m_1 \ddot u_1 + (k_1+k_2) u_1 - k_2 u_2 + m_1 g &= F_1 \\
(m_2 + m_3) \ddot u_2 + m_3 L \ddot \theta \sin \theta + m_3 L \dot \theta^2 \cos \theta - k_2 u_1 + k_2 u_2 + (m_2 + m_3) g &= F_2 + F_3 \sin \theta\\
m_3 \ddot u_2 L \sin \theta + m_3 L^2 \ddot \theta + m_3 g L \sin \theta &= F_3L
\end{cases}
$$

div.style: display: flex; align-items: unsafe center; justify-content: unsafe flex-start; width: 1px; height: 1px; padding-top: 575px; margin-left: 2px;
box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 0px; text-align: left;
display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.2; pointer-events: all; white-space: nowrap;

div.data-content:
## 1.1

由Hamilton原理

$$\int \delta T - \delta V + \delta W_{nc} = 0$$

动能

$$
\begin{align*}
T &= \frac{1}{2}m_1 \dot u_1^2 + \frac{1}{2}m_2 \dot u_2^2 + \frac{1}{2}m_3 (v_{x3}^2 + v_{y3}^2) \\
&= \frac{1}{2}m_1 \dot u_1^2 + \frac{1}{2}m_2 \dot u_2^2 + \frac{1}{2}m_3 ((L \dot \theta \cos \theta)^2 + (\dot u_2 + L \dot \theta \sin \theta)^2) \\
&= \frac{1}{2}m_1 \dot u_1^2 + \frac{1}{2}m_2 \dot u_2^2 + \frac{1}{2}m_3 (\dot u_2^2 + 2 \dot u_2 L \dot \theta \sin \theta + L^2 \dot \theta^2)
\end{align*}
$$

则

$$
\delta T = m_1 \dot u_1 \delta \dot u_1 + m_2 \dot u_2 \delta \dot u_2 + m_3 \dot u_2 \delta \dot u_2 + m_3 L \dot \theta \sin \theta \delta \dot u_2 + m_3 \dot u_2 L \sin \theta \delta \dot \theta + m_3 \dot u_2 L \dot \theta \cos \theta \delta \theta + m_3 L^2 \dot \theta \delta \dot \theta
$$

势能

$$
\begin{align*}
V &= \frac{1}{2} k_1 u_1^2 + \frac{1}{2} k_2 (u_2 - u_1)^2 + m_1 g u_1 + m_2 g u_2 + m_3 g (u_2 - L \cos \theta)
\end{align*}
$$

则

$$
\delta V = k_1 u_1 \delta u_1 + k_2(u_2 - u_1)(\delta u_2 - \delta u_1) + m_1 g \delta u_1 + m_2 g \delta u_2 + m_3 g(\delta u_2 + L \sin \theta \delta \theta)
$$

非保守力做功

$$
\begin{align*}
\delta W_{nc} &= F_1 \delta u_1 + F_2 \delta u_2 + \vec F_3 \cdot \delta \vec r_3 \\
&=F_1 \delta u_1 + F_2 \delta u_2 + (F_3 \cos \theta (L \cos \theta \delta \theta) + F_3\sin\theta (\delta u_2 + L \sin \theta \delta \theta)) \\
&=F_1 \delta u_1 + (F_2 + F_3 \sin \theta) \delta u_2 +
F_3 L\delta \theta \\
\end{align*}
$$

所以

$$
\begin{align*}
\int \delta T - \delta V + \delta W_{nc} &= \int_{t_1}^{t_2} ( m_1 \dot u_1 \delta \dot u_1 + m_2 \dot u_2 \delta \dot u_2 + m_3 \dot u_2 \delta \dot u_2 + m_3 L \dot \theta \sin \theta \delta \dot u_2 + m_3 \dot u_2 L \sin \theta \delta \dot \theta + m_3 \dot u_2 L \dot \theta \cos \theta \delta \theta + m_3 L^2 \dot \theta \delta \dot \theta\\
&\quad - ( k_1 u_1 \delta u_1 + k_2(u_2 - u_1)(\delta u_2 - \delta u_1) + m_1 g \delta u_1 + m_2 g \delta u_2 + m_3 g(\delta u_2 + L \sin \theta \delta \theta) ) \\
&\quad + F_1 \delta u_1 + (F_2 + F_3 \sin \theta) \delta u_2 + F_3 L\delta \theta )d t\\
&= m_1 \dot u_1 \delta u_1 \big |_{t_1}^{t_2} - \int_{t_1}^{t_2}m_1 \ddot u_1 \delta u_1 dt + m_2 \dot u_2 \delta u_2 \big |_{t_1}^{t_2} - \int_{t_1}^{t_2}m_2 \ddot u_2 \delta u_2 dt + m_3 \dot u_2 \delta u_2 \big |_{t_1}^{t_2} - \int_{t_1}^{t_2}m_3 \ddot u_2 \delta u_2 dt \\
&\quad + m_3 L \dot \theta \sin \theta \delta u_2 \big |_{t_1}^{t_2} - \int_{t_1}^{t_2}(m_3 L \ddot \theta \sin \theta + m_3 L \dot \theta^2 \cos \theta) \delta u_2dt \\
&\quad+ m_3 L \dot u_2 \sin \theta \delta \theta \big |_{t_1}^{t_2} - \int_{t_1}^{t_2}(m_3 L \ddot u_2 \sin \theta + m_3 L \dot u_2\dot \theta \cos \theta) \delta \theta dt\\
&\quad + \int_{t_1}^{t_2} m_3 \dot u_2 L \dot \theta \cos \theta \delta \theta d t \\
&\quad + m_3 L^2 \dot \theta \delta \theta \big |_{t_1}^{t_2} - \int_{t_1}^{t_2}m_3 L^2 \ddot \theta \delta \theta dt \\
&\quad \int_{t_1}^{t_2} - ( k_1 u_1 \delta u_1 + k_2(u_2 - u_1)(\delta u_2 - \delta u_1) + m_1 g \delta u_1 + m_2 g \delta u_2 + m_3 g(\delta u_2 + L \sin \theta \delta \theta) ) \\
&\quad + F_1 \delta u_1 + (F_2 + F_3 \sin \theta) \delta u_2 + F_3 L\delta \theta )d t\\
&= -\int_{t_1}^{t_2}(m_1 \ddot u_1 + (k_1+k_2) u_1 - k_2 u_2 + m_1 g - F_1 )dt \\
&\quad - \int_{t_1}^{t_2}((m_2 + m_3) \ddot u_2 + m_3 L \ddot \theta \sin \theta + m_3 L \dot \theta^2 \cos \theta - k_2 u_1 + k_2 u_2 + (m_2 + m_3) g - F_2 - F_3 \sin \theta)dt \\
&\quad -\int_{t_1}^{t_2}(m_3 \ddot u_2 L \sin \theta + m_3 L^2 \ddot \theta + m_3 g L \sin \theta - F_3L)dt \\
&= 0
\end{align*}
$$

由$u_1, u_2, \theta$任意性有

$$
\begin{cases}
m_1 \ddot u_1 + (k_1+k_2) u_1 - k_2 u_2 + m_1 g &= F_1 \\
(m_2 + m_3) \ddot u_2 + m_3 L \ddot \theta \sin \theta + m_3 L \dot \theta^2 \cos \theta - k_2 u_1 + k_2 u_2 + (m_2 + m_3) g &= F_2 + F_3 \sin \theta\\
m_3 \ddot u_2 L \sin \theta + m_3 L \ddot \theta + m_3 g L^2 \sin \theta &= F_3L
\end{cases}
$$

div.style: display: flex; align-items: unsafe center; justify-content: unsafe flex-start; width: 1px; height: 1px; padding-top: 2329px; margin-left: 53px;
box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 0px; text-align: left;
display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.2; pointer-events: all; white-space: nowrap;

div.data-content:
## 1.3

平衡的时候有$\ddot u_1 = \ddot u_2 = \ddot \theta = \dot u_1 = \dot u_2 = \dot \theta = 0$, 代入方程有:

$$
\begin{cases}
(k_1+k_2) u_1 - k_2 u_2 + m_1 g &= F_1 \\
-k_2 u_1 + k_2 u_2 + (m_2 + m_3) g &= F_2 + F_3 \sin \theta\\
m_3 g L \sin \theta &= F_3L
\end{cases}
$$

解得

$$
\begin{cases}
u_1 &= \frac{(F_1 + F_2) m_3 g + F_3^2 - (m_1 + m_2 + m_3)m_3g^2}{k_1 m_3 g} \\
u_2 &= \frac{k_2 F_1 m_3 g + (k_1 + k_2)F_2 m_3 g + (k_1+k_2)F_3^2 - k_2(m_1+m_2+m_3)m_3g^2 - k_1 (m_2+m_3) m_3 g^2}{k_1 k_2 m_3 g}\\
\theta &= \arcsin \frac {F_3} {m_3 g}
\end{cases}
$$

若初始时$F_i= 0$, 则有

$$
\begin{cases}
u_1^\star &= \frac{- (m_1 + m_2 + m_3)g}{k_1} \\
u_2^\star &= \frac{ - k_2(m_1+m_2+m_3)g - k_1 (m_2 + m_3)g}{k_1 k_2}\\
\theta^\star &= 0
\end{cases}
$$
div.p: 平衡的时候有, 代入方程有:

div.data-content:
## 1.4

考虑平衡位置

$$
\begin{cases}
u_1^\star &= \frac{(F_1 + F_2) m_3 g + F_3^2 - (m_1 + m_2 + m_3)m_3g^2}{k_1 m_3 g} \\
u_2^\star &= \frac{k_2 F_1 m_3 g + (k_1 + k_2)F_2 m_3 g + (k_1+k_2)F_3^2 - k_2(m_1+m_2+m_3)m_3g^2 - k_1 (m_2+m_3) m_3 g^2}{k_1 k_2 m_3 g}\\
\theta^\star &= \arcsin \frac {F_3} {m_3 g}
\end{cases}
$$

平衡位置处线性化, 令

$$
\begin{cases}
\hat u_1 &= u_1^\star + u_1 \\
\hat u_2 &= u_2^\star + u_2 \\
\hat \theta &= \theta^\star + \theta
\end{cases}
$$

且有

$$
\begin{align*}
\sin \theta \rightarrow \theta \\
\cos \theta \rightarrow 1 \\
\dot \theta^2 \rightarrow 0 \\
\ddot \theta \theta \rightarrow 0
\end{align*}
$$

化简则有

$$
\begin{cases}
m_1 \ddot u_1 + (k_1+k_2) u_1 - k_2 u_2 &= F_1 \\
(m_2 + m_3) \ddot u_2 - k_2 u_1 + k_2 u_2 &= F_2 + F_3 \sin \theta \\
m_3 L^2 \ddot \theta + m_3 g L \theta &= F_3L
\end{cases}
$$

写出矩阵形式:

$$
\begin{bmatrix}
m_1 & 0 & 0 \\
0 & m_2 + m_3 & 0 \\
0 & 0 & m_3 L^2
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
\ddot u_1 \\
\ddot u_2 \\
\ddot \theta
\end{bmatrix}
+
\begin{bmatrix}
k_1 + k_2 & -k_2 & 0 \\
-k_2 & k_2 & 0 \\
0 & 0 & m_3 g L
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
u_1 \\
u_2 \\
\theta
\end{bmatrix}
=\begin{bmatrix}
F_1 \\
F_2 + F_3 \sin \theta \\
F_3L
\end{bmatrix}
$$

由题意$F_i = 0$

$$
\begin{bmatrix}
m_1 & 0 & 0 \\
0 & m_2 + m_3 & 0 \\
0 & 0 & m_3 L^2
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
\ddot u_1 \\
\ddot u_2 \\
\ddot \theta
\end{bmatrix}
+
\begin{bmatrix}
k_1 + k_2 & -k_2 & 0 \\
-k_2 & k_2 & 0 \\
0 & 0 & m_3 g L
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
u_1 \\
u_2 \\
\theta
\end{bmatrix}
=0
$$


由于$m_i = m, k_i = k$, 则

$$
M = \begin{bmatrix}
m & 0 & 0 \\
0 & 2m & 0 \\
0 & 0 & m L^2
\end{bmatrix}
$$

$$
K = \begin{bmatrix}
2 k & -k & 0 \\
-k & k & 0 \\
0 & 0 & m g L
\end{bmatrix}
$$

特征方程

$$|K - \lambda M | = ( m L^2 \lambda - m g L) (2 m^2 \lambda^2 - 5 k m \lambda + k^2) = 0$$

解得

$$
\begin{cases}
\lambda_1 &= \frac{5 - \sqrt{17} }{4 } \frac{k}{m} \\
\lambda_2 &= \frac{5 + \sqrt{17}}{4 } \frac{k}{m} \\
\lambda_3 &= \frac{g}{L} \\
\end{cases}
$$

特征向量为

$$
\begin{cases}
u_1 &= c_1 \begin{bmatrix}
\frac{-3 + \sqrt{17} }{2} \\
1 \\
0
\end{bmatrix} \\
u_2 &= c_2 \begin{bmatrix}
\frac{-3 - \sqrt{17} }{2} \\
1 \\
0
\end{bmatrix} \\
u_3 &= c_3 \begin{bmatrix}
0 \\
0 \\
1
\end{bmatrix} \\
\end{cases}
$$
